keyFacts: An FBI 302 report (EFTA00154315) was transmitted on February 24, 2021.
The report originated from the FBI New York Field Office's Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking Desk.
The report was sent to the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS).
The email transmission indicates ongoing investigative activity related to child exploitation and human trafficking.
